# ConstructHub - Construction Materials Marketplace

## ğŸ“‹ Project Overview

ConstructHub is a comprehensive digital marketplace that connects construction material suppliers with buyers, contractors, and individual builders. The platform brings all construction materials like bricks, cement, steel, tiles, plumbing, and electrical fittings together in one convenient location.

